\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Stay in Saddle: }{\fs20\cf0 You can react instantly to try to avoid falling when your mount rears or bolts unexpectedly or when you take damage. This usage does not take an action.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Fight with Warhorse: }{\fs20\cf0 If you direct your war-trained mount to attack in battle, you can still make your own attack or attacks normally. This usage is a free action.
