\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Action:}{\fs20\cf0  Trying to gain information with Sense Motive generally takes at least 1 minute, and you could spend a whole evening trying to get a sense of the people around you.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Try Again:}{\fs20\cf0  No, though you may make a Sense Motive check for each Bluff check made against you.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Special:}{\fs20\cf0  A ranger gains a bonus on Sense Motive checks when using this skill against a favored enemy.
\par If you have the Negotiator feat, you get a +2 bonus on Sense Motive checks.
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Synergy:}{\fs20\cf0  If you have 5 or more ranks in Sense Motive, you get a +2 bonus on Diplomacy checks.
